FBIS4-15033 "drsov066_b_94034" FBIS-SOV-94-066 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military Issues Yeltsin Revives Missiles, Artillery Academy Yeltsin Revives Missiles, Artillery Academy LD0504173794 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1600 GMT 5 Apr 94 LD0504173794 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] Boris Yeltsin has signed an edict on the revival of the Russian Academy of Missiles and Artillery Sciences. The intention of the document is to revive traditions of Russian military studies as well as to further research in the defense sector and to train qualified specialists, the presidential press service reports.
